data.text:
The Nikkor Z 180-600mm f/5.6-6.3 VR lens is still out of stock everywhere, but is available on the grey market with a $250 premium

The Nikon NIKKOR Z 180-600mm f/5.6-6.3 VR lens is still out of stock everywhere, but is currently available on the grey market – the third-party seller Electronics Basket has the lens in stock on Amazon for $1,949 ($250 premium, no Nikon USA warranty). The feedback for the seller can be found here.
